 the lead assist had indicated it was ok to do so, this behaviour of course devaluates the monk's abilities.  Sollron is one of the most skillful monks I've had the pleasure of grouping with.  Btw, off topic, Sol we need to go get a Tranix Crown for you sometime, you need that Magic Resist/ac/perma-infravision bad <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   <br>
